headline: NYSE and PDR Services LLC Announce Name Change for Three Exchange-Traded Funds
summary: NEW YORK, January 13, 2026--PDR Services LLC, a wholly-owned subsidiary of Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE: ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, today announced a change to three SPDR exchange-traded fund names as reflected below.
